Evicted Big Brother Naija housemate, Sir Dee has revealed the likely winner of ‘Pepper Dem’ edition. Sir Dee who was evicted on Sunday during the BBNaija live eviction show said Omashola will be the winner. He said this while having a chat with Ebuka Obi-Uchendu on stage after hisveviction from the house. He said: “I think Omashola will win this show.” Meanwhile, 12 housemates are left in the BBNaija house to compete for the grand prize of N60m. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.